			<description><![CDATA[<p>
EMPOWER NY is looking to expand it&#39;s in-house sales team. This position offers a base salary, benefits, expense account, and an aggressive commission structure.</p>
<p>
We offer extensive training in our product and market for any new member of our team.</p>
<p>
<strong>PRIMARY RESPONSIBILITIES:</strong></p>
<p>
All tasks associated with identifying, developing and closing new business including:<br />
Basic prospecting, initial contact, opportunity analysis, and closing.</p>
<p>
&nbsp;</p>
<p>
<strong>ADDITIONAL RESPONSIBILITIES:&nbsp;</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
Calling on leads purchased from lead companies</li>
<li>
Prospecting for leads through trade shows, networking groups, and cold-calling</li>
<li>
Setting appointments to Demonstrate EMPOWER NY to potential clients</li>
<li>
Maintaining strong client relationships to meet their needs and generate referrals</li>
<li>
Meet or exceed monthly sales goals by using proper sales techniques, account management, and problem solving</li>
<li>
Follow up on all assigned leads in a timely professional manner.</li>
<li>
Self-generate leads</li>
<li>
Maintain a thorough knowledge of our products and services</li>
<li>
Prepare proposals</li>
<li>
Use the Customer Relationship Management software and procedures to provide status, follow up, and sales reporting</li>
<li>
Promptly follow up with Customers to determine satisfaction and to acquire leads, referrals, testimonials, and the satisfaction survey</li>
<li>
Perform other duties as assigned</li>
</ul>
<p>
&nbsp;</p>
<p>
<strong>KNOWLEDGE AND SKILL REQUIREMENTS:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
Ability to persuade and influence others. Ability to develop and deliver presentations. Ability to create, compose, and edit written materials. Strong interpersonal and communication skills.</li>
<li>
Visibility requires maintaining a professional appearance and providing a positive company image to the public.</li>
<li>
Work requires significant local travel to current and potential clients.</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
